2023
This year has been an interesting one. I don’t even know where to start and thankfully I’m assuming most people won’t read this because it will be too long and too melodramatic. This year has certainly been one of the most difficult that I can remember. I had such high expectations and hopes. I was hoping my income would surpass or stay the same as last year, I was hoping I’d be less stressed, I was hoping I’d be swimming in modeling gigs. I’ve experienced intense depression that was thankfully punctuated by some really high highs. I was brought back to lessons I learned when I was 16 and 18 years old. When I was 16 I learned not everybody cares about you, at 18 I learned that just because you have everything planned out, that doesn’t mean it’ll happen that way. I also was reacquainted with my strength. Sometimes I forget. This year was filled with so much weird conflict and me shedding relationships with people in my life. I’ll forever look back at this year as the year where everything was trimmed down to the bone. My main source of income gone, people who I thought had my back didn’t, dance who knows where she is anymore. Despite all the weird shit. I know I’ll come out the other side. Everything works out. 
❤️❤️❤️ (If you really read all this, get a life perv) 
🤣🤣🤣 😘😘😘
